Type: Project
Description: R dependencies for the rbartpackages Python project. rbartpackages
    wraps these R BART packages via rpy2; this file lets renv discover and
    install them (including BART3 and missBART, which are not on CRAN) without
    dummy R scripts.
Imports:
    BART,
    BART3,
    bartMachine,
    dbarts,
    missBART
Remotes:
    rsparapa/bnptools/BART3,
    yongchengoh/missBART
